Tiger Woods Commits to Play in U.S PGA Championship Near Atlanta in August

-- B y   M i c h a e l   B u t e a u
-- 
2011-07-29T19:08:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-29/tiger-woods-commits-to-play-in-u-s-pga-championship-near-atlanta-in-august.html
Tiger Woods  has committed to play in
next month’s PGA Championship near Atlanta, tournament officials
said in an e-mail.  Woods, seeking his 15th major title, said yesterday he was
playing in next week’s World Golf Championships event in  Ohio ,
his first tournament in two months as he recovered from knee and
ankle injuries.  The PGA, the season’s final major, is scheduled for Atlanta
Athletic Club Aug. 11-14.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Larry Siddons at 
 lsiddons@bloomberg.net  